     <h2> <img src="http://img.webmd.com/dtmcms/live/webmd/consumer_assets/site_images/modules/actionsetTOC_decsion_pt.jpg" alt="decision point" width="77" height="20" class="headerImg_fmt" />Should I (or my child) have surgery for scoliosis?</h2> 
     <div class="decisionPoint_fmt"> 
      <div class="section_fmt "> 
